{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:46:18.479237+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: aafb1240db602fd1ff16225d59f74ed7c4701151)", "id": "lc_461e9f05-01a6-466a-b475-3a21f321c54e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "<template>\n  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <RouterLink to=\"/\" class=\"navbar-brand\" @click=\"collapseNavbar\">ProjectName</RouterLink>\n      <button\n        :class=\"['navbar-toggler', !navbarExpanded && 'collapsed']\"\n        type=\"button\"\n        aria-controls=\"navbarDefault\"\n        :aria-expanded=\"navbarExpanded\"\n        aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\"\n        @click=\"toggleNavbar\"\n      >\n        <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n      </button>\n\n      <div id=\"navbarDefault\" :class=\"['collapse navbar-collapse', navbarExpanded && 'show']\">\n        <ul class=\"navbar-nav mr-auto\">\n          <li class=\"nav-item\">\n            <RouterLink to=\"/\" class=\"nav-link\" @click=\"collapseNavbar\">Home</RouterLink>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"nav-item\">\n            <RouterLink to=\"/about\" class=\"nav-link\" @click=\"collapseNavbar\">About</RouterLink>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref } from 'vue'\n\ndefineOptions({\n  name: 'DefaultNav',\n})\n\nconst navbarExpanded = ref(false)\n\nconst toggleNavbar = () => {\n  navbarExpanded.value = !navbarExpanded.value\n}\n\nconst collapseNavbar = () => {\n  navbarExpanded.value = false\n}\n</script>\n", "id": "lc_e5b76764-52db-4f79-83bb-b1a100d3b18c"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "bb2337f3-ee05-4487-9cb6-be65e25fb354", "tool_call_id": "call_4b881e065bb44c8c819b37e0", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:46:32.687063+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "```\n\nAnd `DefaultFooter.vue` is included in the layout wrapper as well.\n\n### How the About Page Is Loaded\n\nThe About page has a specific journey through the application:\n\n1. **Route definition**: In `src/router/index.js`, the `/about` route is defined with **lazy loading** (code-splitting):\n   ```js\n   component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: \"about\" */ '../views/About.vue')\n   ```\n   Unlike the Home route (which is eagerly imported at the top of the router file), the About component is only fetched when the user navigates to `/about`. Vite/Webpack will produce a separate chunk file (named `about.[hash].js`) that is downloaded on demand.\n\n2. **Navigation trigger**: When the user clicks \"About\" in the `DefaultNav` component's navbar (`<RouterLink to=\"/about\">`), Vue Router matches the `/about` path and triggers the lazy import.\n\n3. **Chunk download & mount**: The dynamic `import()` fires, fetching the separate JS chunk. Once resolved, Vue Router renders the `About.vue` component as the `<RouterView />` child.\n\n4. **Layout wrapping**: Since the About route's `meta.layout` is `'default'`, the `App.vue` computed property resolves to the `LayoutDefault` component. This wraps the `About.vue` output with the full default layout:\n   ```\n   ┌─ DefaultLayout ──────────────────────┐\n   │  ┌─ DefaultNav ────────────────────┐ │\n   │  │  Navbar with Home / About links  │ │\n   │  └─────────────────────────────────┘ │\n   │                                       │\n   │  <RouterView>                         │\n   │    ┌─ About.vue ──────────────────┐  │\n   │    │  <h1>This is the about page</h1>│ │\n   │    └──────────────────────────────┘  │\n   │  </RouterView>                        │\n   │                                       │\n   │  ┌─ DefaultFooter ─────────────────┐ │\n   │  └─────────────────────────────────┘ │\n   └───────────────────────────────────────┘\n   ```\n\n5. **What About.vue renders**: The component itself is minimal — it simply renders a `<div class=\"container\">` containing an `<h1>` with the text \"This is the about page\". It has no child components, no data fetching, and no additional logic.\n\n### Summary\n\n| Concern | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| **Entry point** | `index.html` → `/src/main.js` |\n| **App shell** | `App.vue` — dynamic layout component + `<RouterView />` |\n| **Routing** | `vue-router` with hash history, 2 routes (`/` and `/about`) |\n| **Layout system** | Route `meta.layout` → dynamic `<component :is=\"layout\">` resolution → globally registered `LayoutDefault` |\n| **Default layout** | `Default.vue` with `<DefaultNav>`, `<slot>` (page content), `<DefaultFooter>` |\n| **About page** | Lazy-loaded via dynamic `import()`, renders a simple heading inside the default layout |", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 691, "prompt_tokens": 11987, "total_tokens": 12678, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 1, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 11200, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000983835, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000382665, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00060117}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780962378-C4ziGz5ohzKNxeLoOAlK", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9a1-42f0-7152-82fd-38c314eaea25-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11987, "output_tokens": 691, "total_tokens": 12678, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11200}, "output_token_details": 